; }&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://sam-osian.com/2025/07/14/rethinking-statistical-significance/</link> <pubDate>Fri, 11 Jul 2025 15:23:05 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://sam-osian.com/feed_rss_created.xml">Sam Osian — Health Data Scientist</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://sam-osian.com/2025/07/14/rethinking-statistical-significance/</guid> <enclosure url="https://sam-osian.com/assets/images/social/posts/rethinking-significance.png" type="image/png" length="46614" /> </item> </channel></rss>